      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S LOKI (1) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (20.13) behind Sunlit Amber at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. One of the contenders. SASSY SANDY (5) was a strong winner (20.17) from box 3 last time, scoring by 2.75 lengths at this track. Has a tricky draw to overcome and will need a clean break. Can make it two on the bounce. FINS UP WENDY (7) hasn't been far away here at the last two, finding the frame both times, most recently when third beaten 4 lengths (20.32). Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. SERENA BEACH (2) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
